WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Being in a moment of reduced mobility,
with pain or discomfort from a health condition

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.500
or recovering from a procedure
is not a pleasant experience.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.000
That is why we created Hypnos —
a cushion that lets you rest safely

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.500
and makes it easier to perform movements
like lying on your side.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Hypnos keeps your legs parallel
and your hip in a neutral position.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:37.000
It prevents one leg from rotating over the other,
reducing the risk of dislocation.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:43.000
It also reduces load on the knee joint
and relieves muscle tension —

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:48.000
giving you a sense of
wellbeing and relaxation.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:56.000
If a family member or healthcare professional
is assisting you,

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:01.000
always introduce the leg
with less mobility first.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:07.500
We are here to support
your recovery.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Hypnos — the cushion that not only
transforms your nights,

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:20.000
but also provides support and comfort.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000
Experience the difference of true rest.
